{
  "stem": "3150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You didn't know anything else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's just survival, you know, sleep, get up, and then, you know-- and then, when it came to New Years of the end of '43, [INAUDIBLE] was a lot of noise.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Russians are coming back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're coming back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- But then for some reason they stopped, you know, and it took, like-- but finally in February, they, they passed us through.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they stopped in that little village where we used to get our food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the minute they got there, we, we all went, picked up, and went to that village.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He told us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, the guy-- the Russians are here, the-- they're here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're, and they're right there, and they're-- and the army's there, and the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we picked up, and we went to the guy that used to give us the food.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were right in the same town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, they were in his house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they, they took his house for some command or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they treated us very good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Can't complain, and we knew they were-- they had to leave, too, because it was the front line.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they gave us an escort at that time and took us to Luck, to that city.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when we got to Luck--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they put us-- they gave us transportation with horses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took us to Luck.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we got to Luck, there was some semblance of our Jewish organization.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They, they put you up, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went to their office, and there was a lot of bombed-out places, so they gave us an apartment.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we stayed there a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
